1. *Zapravo* samo želim da znam istinu. (I just want to know the truth.)
2. On je *zapravo* veoma pametan. (He is actually very smart.)
3. *Zapravo*, to nije tačno. (Actually, that is not true.)
4. *Zapravo*, nismo ni mislili da je to moguće. (Actually, we didn't even think it was possible.)
5. *Zapravo*, to je još gore. (Actually, it's even worse.)